title: #71 - Stable Ronaldo Calls Out NRG Clix to a Boxing Match
itunes:title: #71 - Stable Ronaldo Calls Out NRG Clix to a Boxing Match
description: On this episode of The CouRage and Nadeshot Show podcast, Stable Ronaldo comes onto the show as a guest and talks about living in the NRG Fortnite House with Clix, quitting competitive Fortnite, playing on the OfflineTV Rust Server, winning a $50k tournament, and more!
